Revision history for Dancer-Plugin-Auth-Htpasswd

0.020     2014-04-12
          Switched to using Dist::Zilla.

0.014     2012-06-16
          Fixed version number in README files.

0.013     2012-06-16
          * The REMOTE_USER request variable is now set upon authorization
          * Static files are now properly protected

0.012     2012-01-15
          * Fixed the problem with README file generation during build process
          * Authorization information is now read from a request header, not an
            environment variable

0.011     2011-11-13
          Added missing requirements to build script.

0.01      2011-10-10
          First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
